Linux
-----

To compile and install on linux run:

	sudo make

This will install everything in /usr/local/bin and /usr/local/man/man.1.



Mac OS X
--------

To compile and install on Mac OS X you must first install the following
libraries:

gdbm (http://www.gnu.org.ua/software/gdbm/)
zlib (http://www.zlib.net)
libpng (http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/libpng.html)
jpeg (http://libjpeg.sourceforge.net) (remember to sudo make install-lib)
gd (http://www.boutell.com/gd/)
freetype (http://sourceforge.net/projects/freetype/files)


Windows
-------

Install MingW (gcc + make), then run:

	make

This will install everything into c:\opt\bin.



All
---

Tweak everything in Common.mk ...



